        <p class="mb-4">A well-designed lobby mural or feature wall is one of the most powerful statements a business can make about its brand. When clients and visitors walk into your space and see a large-format wall graphic that captures the personality and values of your company, it sets the tone for the entire interaction, and many of our clients extend that brand statement to their storefront with matching <a href="/signs/business-signs/window-signs" class="link-notification">window signs</a> and exterior banners. We have produced lobby graphics for businesses across the Chicagoland area that range from simple logo installations on a painted accent wall to full-scale photographic murals, and for clients who need a professional logo built before we print our <a href="/design-services/logo-design" class="link-notification">logo design</a> team creates scalable vector artwork ready for large-format wall application.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">Our large-format printing equipment handles wall graphics at virtually any scale, from a small quote above a desk to a floor-to-ceiling mural across a feature wall. We match colors precisely to your brand standards and we can work from your existing artwork or create something new specifically for your space, and for interior privacy treatments that complement your mural see our <a href="/signs/business-signs/door-signs" class="link-notification">frosted door signs</a> that give conference rooms and office spaces a polished privacy finish.</p>
        <p>Need a logo built for large-format wall application? Our <a href="/design-services/logo-design" class="link-notification">logo design</a> team creates scalable vector artwork. Our <a href="/design-services/graphic-design" class="link-notification">graphic design</a> team can also lay out full-wall murals ready for production. <a href="/signs/business-signs/door-signs" class="link-notification">Door signs</a> with matching fonts and colors tie your lobby and entrance graphics together. We serve the full Chicagoland area including Joliet, Shorewood, Crest Hill, Romeoville, Plainfield, Lockport, and New Lenox. Call us at <a href="tel:+18153498600" class="link-notification">(815) 349-8600</a> to schedule a consultation for your wall sign or mural project today.</p>
